pendency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"org.sonatype.plexus:plexus-build-api:0.0.7\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"The Mojo uses Plexus BuildContext injection for incremental/up-to-date tracking.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"com.diffplug.spotless:spotless-lib:2.45.0\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"The plugin exposes and executes Spotless formatter types from spotless-lib, which are runtime dependencies rather than compile API dependencies.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"com.diffplug.spotless:spotless-lib-extra:2.45.0\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"The Maven plugin delegates many formatter implementations to spotless-lib-extra, published as a runtime dependency.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Exercise the Maven plugin as a Mojo against temporary files: configure a simple format or Java/POM formatter with built-in steps such as trimTrailingWhitespace/endWithNewline/licenseHeader, initialize Maven-injected fields like project, baseDir, buildDir, goal, ResourceManager, and BuildContext, then run apply/check and assert file changes or failures. Avoid formatter steps that require external tools, npm/go binaries, or downloading formatter artifacts unless explicitly provisioned.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Private Maven-injected fields may require reflection or a small test helper to initialize correctly.\",\n    \"Some Spotless formatter steps provision external artifacts or tools; those can make tests network-sensitive and should be avoided for baseline coverage.\",\n    \"Native Image verification may still require metadata for Maven/Plexus/JGit paths reached by the chosen test.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06add6cff3c3bdec016a28674816bc81939b30907ca925bb79\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3181, "output": 867, "cacheRead": 33280, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 37328, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781032768126, "responseId": "resp_06add6cff3c3bdec016a286740b5f481939ec6ecbd03b46a04"}}
